      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then add it<strong> </strong>to the pan and cook, covered, for 2-3 min further or until the spinach has wilted and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced beef filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
