      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>spiced beef filling</strong> between the <strong>tortillas </strong>(make sure to only cover one half of the tortilla with the filling!)</p><p>Break the <strong>feta</strong> up into small pieces on the top of the filling</p><p>Fold each tortilla over so you're left with 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12] </span>half moon-shaped sandwiches – these are your <strong>spiced Turkish-style beef, spinach & feta flatbreads</strong></p>",
